Prerequsite to install Ansible is Python

Commands To Install Ansible are 
 1) sudo apt update -y
 2) sudo apt install software-properties-common
 3) sudo add-apt-repository --yes --update ppa:ansible/ansible
 4) sudo apt install ansible


----> Steps to configure the Ansible in UBUNTU SERVER <----

* We have to create the Inventory file and add the all Private DNS in that Inventory file 
  then,
 we can access all thy Client Servers using the Master Ansible Server i.e, To upgrade any Patch to the 
 Client Servers

* By Creating the Playbooks we can Do any kind of the activity
